You are in 2\S and need only eight tricks. Count the tops: your trump suit is worth five winners once drawn, and you have three more top tricks outside, which already totals the eight you need. There is nothing to develop and no finesse to risk; just cash what you own. NS hold 21 of the 40 points, so the defense has 19, and with neither opponent bidding, no one holds a surprise long suit.

